TEST CASES as an EXAMPLE
test case number 123-75
TITLE:
Koel app | Info panel (Lyrics, Artist, Album) |Lyrics should be displayed for a playing song

Description
GIVEN The user is logged in
AND on the 'All songs' page
AND selected song is reproducing

Test Step
1 WHEN user clicks om INFO button on the music player
Expected Result
THEN INFO panel with tags "Lyrics", "Artist", "Album" appears

2 AND the user select the "Lyrics" tag
Expected Result
THEN lyrics of the song appears in the "Lyrics" field of the INFO panel




